LightningCash Build Instructions
--------------------------------

---> Compile from Ubuntu 18.04

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Windows 64 :
------------

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install build-essential libtool autotools-dev automake pkg-config libssl-dev libevent-dev bsdmainutils python3 curl

sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev

sudo apt-get install software-properties-common

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:bitcoin/bitcoin

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install libdb4.8-dev libdb4.8++-dev

sudo apt-get install libminiupnpc-dev

sudo apt-get install libzmq3-dev

sudo apt-get install libqt5gui5 libqt5core5a libqt5dbus5 qttools5-dev qttools5-dev-tools libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler

sudo apt-get install libqrencode-dev

sudo apt install git

git clone https://github.com/MerlinMagic2018/Lightning-Cash

cd Lightning-Cash

cd depends

make HOST=x86_64-w64-mingw32 -j4

cd ..

./autogen.sh

./configure --disable-bench --disable-tests --disable-gui-tests --prefix=$PWD/depends/x86_64-w64-mingw32

make -j4

Done.

daemon, cli and tx in src folder, GUI ( qt ) in src/qt folder.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Windows 32
----------

install docker, and install ubuntu 14.04 in a container

adduser username

usermod -aG sudo username

su - username

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install build-essential libtool autotools-dev automake pkg-config libssl-dev libevent-dev bsdmainutils python3

sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev

sudo apt-get install software-properties-common

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:bitcoin/bitcoin

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install libdb4.8-dev libdb4.8++-dev

sudo apt-get install libminiupnpc-dev

sudo apt-get install libzmq3-dev

sudo apt-get install libqt5gui5 libqt5core5a libqt5dbus5 qttools5-dev qttools5-dev-tools libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler

sudo apt-get install libqrencode-dev

sudo apt-get install git

sudo apt-get install curl

sudo apt install g++-mingw-w64-i686 mingw-w64-i686-dev

git clone https://github.com/MerlinMagic2018/Lightning-Cash

cd Lightning-Cash

cd depends

make HOST=i686-w64-mingw32 -j4

cd ..

./autogen.sh

./configure --disable-bench --disable-tests --disable-gui-tests --prefix=$PWD/depends/i686-w64-mingw32

make -j4

Done.

daemon, cli and tx in src folder, GUI ( qt ) in src/qt folder.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

OSX ( Apple )
----------

install docker, and install ubuntu 14.04 in a container

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install build-essential libtool autotools-dev automake pkg-config libssl-dev libevent-dev bsdmainutils python3

sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev

sudo apt-get install software-properties-common

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:bitcoin/bitcoin

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install libdb4.8-dev libdb4.8++-dev

sudo apt-get install libminiupnpc-dev

sudo apt-get install libzmq3-dev

sudo apt-get install libqt5gui5 libqt5core5a libqt5dbus5 qttools5-dev qttools5-dev-tools libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler

sudo apt-get install libqrencode-dev

sudo apt-get install git

sudo apt-get install curl librsvg2-bin libtiff-tools bsdmainutils cmake imagemagick libcap-dev libz-dev libbz2-dev python-setuptools

git clone https://github.com/MerlinMagic2018/Lightning-Cash

cd Lightning-Cash

cd depends

mkdir SDKs

cd SDKs

sudo apt install wget

wget https://github.com/phracker/MacOSX-SDKs/releases/download/10.13/MacOSX10.11.sdk.tar.xz

tar -xf MacOSX10.11.sdk.tar.xz

cd ..

make HOST=x86_64-apple-darwin11 -j4

cd ..

./autogen.sh

./configure --prefix=$PWD/depends/x86_64-apple-darwin11 --disable-tests --disable-bench --disable-gui-tests

make -j4

Done.

daemon, cli and tx in src folder, GUI ( qt ) in src/qt folder.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Linux :
------


sudo apt-get install build-essential libtool autotools-dev automake pkg-config libssl-dev libevent-dev bsdmainutils python3

sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev

sudo apt-get install software-properties-common

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:bitcoin/bitcoin

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install libdb4.8-dev libdb4.8++-dev

sudo apt-get install libminiupnpc-dev

sudo apt-get install libzmq3-dev

sudo apt-get install libqt5gui5 libqt5core5a libqt5dbus5 qttools5-dev qttools5-dev-tools libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler

sudo apt-get install libqrencode-dev

sudo apt-get install git

sudo apt-get install curl

git clone https://github.com/MerlinMagic2018/Lightning-Cash

cd Lightning-Cash

cd depends

make HOST=x86_64-pc-linux-gnu

cd ..

./autogen.sh

./configure --disable-tests --disable-bench --disable-gui-tests --prefix=$PWD/depends/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu

make -j4

sudo make install

Done.

Binaries in depends/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu/bin/

You need both the "bin" and the "lib" folders, together in a folder, for the binaries to work.

